HOWTO Install screenr from GitHub
---------------------------------

1.  Start an R session.

2.  Install package devtools, if not already installed:

    install.packages("devtools")

3.  Attach devtools:

    library(devtools)

4. Install screenr from GitHub:

    devtools::install_github("sgutreuter/screenr")

5.  Attach screenr and proceed:

    library(screenr)
    ?screenr
